Nigerian singers, MC Galaxy and Skales on Thursday took to social media to verbally assault and threaten each other. The musicians threatened to beat up each other. It all started after Skales called out MC Galaxy on his Instagram story. His post read: “One day I go beat that stupid smelling Mc Galaxy, F*ck boy.” It is not clear why Skales called out MC Galaxy threatening to beat him up. However, MC Galaxy responding said he was up for anything and ready to fight Skales. MC Galaxy wrote: “Broke boys way dey collect money from women can make noise sha. Let me know when you are ready for the fight idi*t, berger.”